      "outcome": "The cipher scripture is completed and consecrated. The Silent Spire's transmissions can now only be interpreted by Keepers fluent in the Unspoken Tongue — even if the Signal-House Families or any other faction were to intercept the Spire's acoustic output, the pronouncements would appear as meaningless harmonic noise without the interpretive framework. The Keepers add a new protective layer: the scripture itself contains embedded acoustic counter-signatures that will trigger the jamming array if any unauthorized attempt to decode it is detected. The Spire's secrets are now doubly protected — by physical isolation and by linguistic obscurity.",
